---
import defaultImage from "../assets/default.webp";

const bannerImg = defaultImage.src;
---

<section
  class="relative flex min-h-[692px] w-full items-center justify-center px-6 py-16"
>
  <img
    src={bannerImg}
    alt=""
    class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>

  <div
    class="relative z-10 flex w-full max-w-4xl flex-col items-center gap-8 text-center text-white"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-5xl lg:text-[60px] lg:leading-[60px]"
    >
      Tu Puerta a la Aventura en Peru
    </h2>

    <p
      class="w-full max-w-[600px] text-base font-medium leading-7 tracking-[0.2px] md:text-[18px] md:leading-[26px]"
    >
      Descubre la majestuosidad de Machu Picchu con nuestra agencia. Te
      ofrecemos visitas guiadas, rutas de trekking y experiencias autenticas
      para que vivas la historia inca de manera inolvidable.
    </p>

    <p
      class="w-full max-w-[600px] text-base font-medium leading-7 tracking-[0.2px] md:text-[18px] md:leading-[26px]"
    >
      Descubre
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8">
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-[#aa5c00] px-4 py-2 text-[18px] font-medium leading-[26px] tracking-[0.2px] text-white transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:opacity-95 hover:shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(170,92,0,0.35)]"
      >
        Ver tours
        <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>

      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-black px-4 py-2 text-[18px] font-medium leading-[26px] tracking-[0.2px] text-white transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-neutral-900 hover:shadow-[0_10px_24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)]"
      >
        Tour destacado
        <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
